OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be
OL,6,Fmostly cloudy during the evening and
OL,7,Fovernight with a few light showers
OL,8,Faround. Some clear spells are then
OL,9,Fexpected to develop later.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FThe odd shower around at
OL,12,Ffirst, otherwise a largely dry day
OL,13,Fwith good sunny spells. A few showers
OL,14,Farriving in the evening.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FA
OL,17,Fmixture of sunshine and showers on
OL,18,FTuesday and Wednesday. Longer spells
OL,19,Fof rain possible on Thursday. Feeling
OL,20,Frather cool for the time of year.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
